    exampleCalculation: "Example 1 (The Conflicted Personality): You were born on August 15th, making you a proud, outgoing Leo Sun. However, you often feel incredibly shy, emotional, and introverted. The calculator reveals you have a Cancer Moon (deeply sensitive) and a Virgo Rising (analytical and reserved). This explains the profound conflict between your core ego and your emotional instincts. Example 2 (The Fast-Changing Ascendant): You were born in Manila at 6:15 AM on October 1st. The calculator determines your Rising sign is Libra. Your twin sister was born at 6:45 AM. By that time, the Earth had rotated enough that the constellation Scorpio had crossed the eastern horizon. Despite being twins born 30 minutes apart, she has a Scorpio Rising, giving her a completely different, much more intense outward aura than your diplomatic Libra persona. Precision is everything in astrological calculation.",
